{"meal_name":"Quinoa Chickpea Buddha Bowl","difficulty_level":"Medium","servings":2,"researched_ingredients":["1/2 cup dry chickpeas (or 1 can, 15 oz, drained)","1/2 cup dry white quinoa","1/2 large bunch curly/dinosaur kale (about 4-5 cups chopped)","1/4 cup tahini","2 tablespoons olive oil (divided)","1/2 teaspoon garlic powder (divided)","1 large lemon (about 3 tablespoons juice)","1/2 teaspoon sea salt (plus to taste)","1/4 teaspoon black pepper (optional)","2-3 tablespoons warm water (for dressing consistency)"]}